<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        /* General styling */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            text-align: left;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #3498db;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }

        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Our Lost and Found Portal is dedicated to helping people recover their lost items
           and connect with those who have found them.</p>
        <p>We serve the community by providing a centralized platform for lost and found items.
           Our mission is to help reunite people with their lost belongings and make the
           process as simple as possible.</p>
        <h3>Our Services</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Report lost items</li>
            <li>Report found items</li>
            <li>Search database of lost and found items</li>
            <li>Connect item finders with owners</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
